OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,FExclusive figures obtained by ITV
OL,7,FBorder show that an average of two
OL,8,Foperations were cancelled each day at
OL,9,Fthe Cumberland Infirmary in 2024.
OL,11,FIn total, 735 operations were
OL,12,Fcancelled on the day of or after
OL,13,Fhospital admission last year. Patients
OL,14,Fsay they felt "left in limbo" as they
OL,15,Fwaited for a new appointment.
OL,17,FThe figures:
OL,19,FOther reasons included patient choice,
OL,20,Fmedical decision or because of a lack
OL,21,Fof available equipment or failure.
