OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,FRhona Wilson, from Workington, says
OL,7,Fshe faced long delays in receiving the
OL,8,Fsurgery she needed.
OL,10,FThe 45-year-old is in remission from
OL,11,Fcervical cancer, but radiotherapy left
OL,12,Fher with digestive issues and a
OL,13,Fruptured bowel.
OL,15,FShe later found out she had an
OL,16,Finfection in her uterus, which led to
OL,17,Fit filling with waste, which she says
OL,18,Fwas extremely painful.
