OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,FOn June 9th 2024, she called an
OL,7,Fambulance to her home after
OL,8,Fexperiencing excruciating uterine
OL,9,Fspasms.
OL,11,FAfter spending two weeks in the
OL,12,Fhospital, Rhona wasn't operated on
OL,13,Funtil 17 July 2024.
OL,15,FShe eventually discharged herself and
OL,16,Fsaid she would drive an hour every day
OL,17,Fto see if her surgery would happen
OL,18,Fthat day.
