OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,FShe told ITV Border: "It got to the
OL,7,Fpoint where every day I was saying
OL,8,Feither 'fix me or kill me, but make
OL,9,Fthe pain stop'.
OL,11,F"I was put on nil by mouth every
OL,12,Fmorning about midnight and then at
OL,13,Flunchtime taken off it. It got to the
OL,14,Fpoint where I actually discharged
OL,15,Fmyself so I could have my medication
OL,16,Fat the right time because that was
OL,17,Fbeing late, and I was in a lot of pain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
