OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,F"I was eventually driving myself,
OL,7,Fwhile on my medication daily, to the
OL,8,Fhospital to see if my operation was
OL,9,Fgoing to happen that day. I did that,
OL,10,Fand I think on the fifth day they
OL,11,Fsaid, 'about 1:30pm, we're going to do
OL,12,Fyour operation'. So, just a month from
OL,13,Fwhen I originally had my pain, I
OL,14,Ffinally got it dealt with.
OL,16,F"Something needs to be done before
OL,17,Fsomebody, bless them, suffers worse
OL,18,Fthan I did."
