OL,6,FIn a statement, the North Cumbria
OL,7,FIntegrated Care NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,8,Fwho run the Cumberland Infirmary,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We understand how frustrating
OL,10,Fit is for patients and their families
OL,11,Fwhen their operations are cancelled,
OL,12,Fparticularly on the same day.
OL,14,F"For that reason, we do everything we
OL,15,Fcan to accommodate the patients on the
OL,16,Fday. Cancelling the operation is
OL,17,Falways a last resort, and a decision
OL,18,Fwe don't take lightly.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
