OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,F"The most common reason for a
OL,7,Fcancellation in 2024 is where lists
OL,8,Foverrun (153). This can happen for a
OL,9,Fnumber of reasons, such as earlier
OL,10,Fprocedures being more complex than
OL,11,Fexpected.
OL,13,F"Other reasons include where the
OL,14,Fpatient did not attend or the patient
OL,15,Fchooses not to go ahead (82) or their
OL,16,Fcondition means it is unsuitable to go
OL,17,Fahead (87).
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
