OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, some will be cancelled
OL,7,Fdue to staff sickness, as our theatre
OL,8,Fcolleagues will experience sickness
OL,9,Fthroughout the year, and often
OL,10,Fprocedures require multiple staff to
OL,11,Fgo ahead.
OL,13,F"We always prioritise cancer and
OL,14,Fclinically urgent procedures, and if
OL,15,Fthese are unavoidably cancelled, we
OL,16,Faim to rebook these as soon as
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
