OL,3,CPatients 'left in limbo' as operations
OL,4,Ccancelled on same day as surgery date
OL,6,F"We are making significant
OL,7,Fimprovements in reducing the number of
OL,8,Foperations that are cancelled on the
OL,9,Fday in 2025, and our theatre
OL,10,Futilisation rate has now increased to
OL,11,F77.8% in May 2025.
OL,13,F"As part of our improvement plans, we
OL,14,Fare also establishing an elective care
OL,15,Fhub at West Cumberland Hospital that
OL,16,Fwill minimise disruptions to planned
OL,17,Foperations across North Cumbria.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
