OL,6,F"We are also trialling having 'stand
OL,7,Fby' patients for some specialities
OL,8,Fthat we can call upon if a theatre
OL,9,Fslot becomes available as part of our
OL,10,Fplans to improve the service we offer
OL,11,Fto the local population."
